file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: api-test
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
    description: dev
paths:
  /posts:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: page
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
      responses:
        '200':
          description: No Content
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object

  /dont_allow_additional_parameter:
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              additionalProperties: false
              required:
                - only_param
              properties:
                only_param:
                  type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: No Content
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
